# Getting Started

InorigoJS is a library built to simplify communication with Inorigo web services. The library is developed and maintained by Ortelius. The library is continuously under development, and will continue to see major improvements in the coming years, both in terms of functionality, performance and documentation.

Are you missing something? Consider contributing to the code base over on Github!
